- read_exact, read_to_end, read_to_string
- write_all, write_all_buf
- copy, copy_bidirectional
- split (into reader + writer)

## Buffered Types
- BufReader<R>
- BufWriter<W>
- BufStream<RW>

## Cancel-Safety Integration
- Reads: cancelable at any point (partial discard OK)
- Writes: two-phase with WritePermit
- Copy: tracks progress, can resume

## Adapters
- Chain, Take, Limit
- Repeat, Empty, Sink
